>http://flagspot.net/flags/jp(k.html

Yes it's great! This is just the kind of thing I was looking for.
Thanks.

FWIW that (in the url confused my email software. The link appears to
end at .../jp and the (k.html portion does not appear to be part of
the link. If anyone else is in the same situation, copy-and-paste the
whole link - all the way through "html". That did the trick for me.

--
Jay Kelly
